-- Deutsche Post sees oper profit up more than 8 pct a year
-- By Marilyn Gerlach
-- Wed Apr 02, 2014 01:09AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, April 2 (Reuters) - Deutsche Post <DPWGn.DE>, the world No. 1 postal and logistics company, unveiled medium-term financial targets through 2020, forecasting that operating profit will grow by an average of more than 8 percent a year.

